<p>XmlRpc now checks if the Http Client has an uri set and does not overwrite it in doRequest(). Two testcases have been added that check if the uri is delegated on doRequest to the client if NONE has been specified yet. And another TestCase that the HttpClient Uri is not overwritten if its already set.</p>

